Seve:

395
00:51:17,520 --> 00:51:21,570
Seve: What really gives
you the perception of the distance

396
00:51:21,760 --> 00:51:24,730
and the feel, is if you swing and you close your eyes.

397
00:51:24,880 --> 00:51:26,325
Seve:

398
00:51:30,920 --> 00:51:32,490
(hit)

399
00:51:34,760 --> 00:51:36,330
(hit)

