00:57:43,800 --> 00:57:48,249
Seve: When I have my three iron,
this is how I create all these shots.

464
00:57:49,400 --> 00:57:53,086
And all the ideas develop
In your imagination when you play.

465
00:57:54,560 --> 00:57:57,689
That's why I am always very sharp and very quick

466
00:57:57,840 --> 00:58:03,847
in finding out the way to escape
to produce those miracle shots.

467
00:58:07,080 --> 00:58:09,162
(music becomes more rhythmic)

468
00:58:26,480 --> 00:58:30,041
(hit)

469
00:58:31,040 --> 00:58:32,610
(applause)

470
00:58:32,760 --> 00:58:35,889
Broadcaster:
He still has magic in his hands...

471
00:58:36,040 --> 00:58:38,088
Rafa:

472
00:58:38,280 --> 00:58:39,441
Seve:

473
00:58:47,720 --> 00:58:48,767
(hit)

474
00:58:49,840 --> 00:58:51,410
(hit)

475
00:58:59,560 --> 00:59:00,104
Brother:

476
00:59:11,400 --> 00:59:12,925
Yeah!

477
00:59:25,240 --> 00:59:26,765
(music builds up)

478
00:59:29,760 --> 00:59:34,926
Broadcaster: In she goes! 65 strokes!
Seve is the champion.

479
00:59:36,120 --> 00:59:38,487
(applause)

480
00:59:55,880 --> 00:59:58,201
(applause)

